sources.description:
After Chernobyl (Ghosts Of Chernobyl) - A group of American tourists travel across Eastern Europe. By accident, they get to Chernobyl, where they face some local evil. It turns out that not all inhabitants of the 'Exclusion Zone' are dead and they try to get out of the city alive.
Stars: Michael Golodini, Catherine Badalyan, Vladimir Dykhovichnyy
